title: "LLM Wiki"
abstract: "LLM Wiki is a persistent, cumulative wiki system that uses LLM agents to import, structure, cross-reference, and maintain a knowledge base from new source materials. The project serves as a template for building personal (or team) LLM-driven knowledge bases with support for linting, queries, and cascading updates."
repository-code: "https://github.com/BogdanovychA/llm-wiki"
